Q.  Server Side Scripting = 
A.  Server Side Scripting excutes on server and database.
    Update a field when record is inserted.
    Setting a value on a field when parent record is updated.
    Valiadate the logged in user.
    Generate Events.
    Send Emails.

    Where to use it -
    ACL
    Business Rule
    Script Include
    Transform Maps
    Workflow

    Server side classes-
    Glide Record-
    It is used for database operation.
    It is used only in server side.
    Synatx - create instance of Glide Record.
    var gr = new Glide Record(<Table Name>);
    Use-Case:
    If we want to create, update, insert, delete some records.

    Glide System - 
    It is used to get information about system and current logged in user.
    It is referred by a variable 'gs'.
    Syntax - gs.<GlideSystemMethod>

    Glide Aggregate -
    Is is used to perform aggregation operation on the database.
    It is extension of GlideRecord class.
    It provide database aggregation- [ COUNT, SUM, MIN, MAX, AVG ] Queries.
    Syntax - var agg = new GlideRecord('incident');
    It is an extension of Glide Record class.
    Glide DateTime,
    Glide Element.

    Fix Script - It is open coding platform where if you have some tasks.
    Ex - If we have to update one lakh records of incidents.
    https://dev347964.service-now.com/now/nav/ui/classic/params/target/sys_script_fix.do%3Fsys_id%3D085b9090c3fda210dbc11c65e4013197%26sysparm_view%3D%26sysparm_domain%3Dnull%26sysparm_domain_scope%3Dnull%26sysparm_record_row%3D2%26sysparm_record_rows%3D834%26sysparm_record_list%3DORDERBYDESCsys_created_on 
    
